tool_description: An API to show top ranking market performers in PSX
title: Pakistan Stock Exchange Data Portal

api_list.name: Get Top 3 Performers
api_list.description: This endpoint returns the current top 3 market performers in all categories.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://pakistan-stock-exchange-data-portal.p.rapidapi.com/psx/top-3"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "pakistan-stock-exchange-data-portal.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
